node.text:
We look chilled and cool, right? Don’t be fooled. Just finished signing 4000 copies of OTK: Shelf Love in 3.5 hours. That’s 1142.85 books per hour, but who’s counting.. Actually, a personal best for @noorishbynoor and me. We definitely have our eyes on Paris 2024 now. 
Also got a tour by the lovely people at @penguinrandomhouse warehouse, where among 30,000 pallets of books we found another old favourite, @ixta.belfrage. 
#OTK #ottolenghitestkitchen
